Class RDFParser

java.lang.Object
  to.networld.scrawler.common.RDFParser
Direct Known Subclasses:
Buddy, Dive, DOAPOrganization, MetaData, Person
public class RDFParser
extends java.lang.Object

Superclass that hiddes the low level RDF parsing code. Each class that needs to parse RDF files should extend from this class.

Author:
Alex Oberhauser
